input.name: AC and PPC Local Excitatory Influence
input.citation: AC and PPC Local Excitatory Influence (2024). (Version draft) [Data set]. DANDI archive. https://dandiarchive.org/dandiset/000936/draft
input.description: Single E neurons were excited via C1V1 using spiral scans of a 1040nm 2P laser. GCaMP6f fluorescence changes were monitored in neighboring cells which were with SOM+ (tdTomato+) or Non-SOM. Mice were running spontaneously on a spherical treadmill. Data were collected from auditory cortex (AC) and posterior parietal cortex (PPC) in each mouse.
